headline.print_headline: Yellen Praises Women's Contributions to Economy
headline.main: Yellen Praises Women's Contributions to Economy

lead_paragraph: The first woman to head the Federal Reserve in its 100-year history says America's economic success over the past century has been due in large part to greater contributions by women.
